title: metric with duration edges
metric_query: select count(*) from {var__my_table} where  duration >= {var__lower_limit} and duration <= {var__upper_limit} and {CORE_FILTERS} and {TRP_FILTERS};
group_by_1_query: select {var__group_by_1}, count(*) from {var__my_table} where {CORE_FILTERS} and {TRP_FILTERS}  and duration >= {var__lower_limit} and duration <= {var__upper_limit} group by {var__group_by_1};
group_by_2_query: select {var__group_by_1}, {var__group_by_2}, count(*) from {var__my_table} where {CORE_FILTERS} and {TRP_FILTERS} and duration >= {var__lower_limit} and duration <= {var__upper_limit} group by {var__group_by_1}, {var__group_by_2};
